                            "content": "<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/d/d72916d9ec1f9ca734c26679d2ecc3941402191e.png\" class=\"height-151-pixels width-128-pixels float-right\"/></p>\n<p>Hier vind je de Kennisbanken die horen bij deze opdracht.</p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<table cellpadding=\"5\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/d/d72916d9ec1f9ca734c26679d2ecc3941402191e.png\" class=\"height-41-pixels width-35-pixels\"/></td>\n<td>\n<h4><a class=\"content-link-button\" href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/110340\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '', 'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=yes,dependent=no,width=900,height=660'); return false;\">Uiteenzetting</a></h4>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<table cellpadding=\"5\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/d/d72916d9ec1f9ca734c26679d2ecc3941402191e.png\" class=\"height-41-pixels width-35-pixels\"/></td>\n<td>\n<h4><a class=\"content-link-button\" href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/110265\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '', 'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=yes,dependent=no,width=900,height=660'); return false;\">Betoog</a></h4>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
